com.robotgame.gameengine.Robot.Builder

Class RobotBlueprint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.robotgame.gameengine.Robot.Builder.RobotBlueprint

  • public class RobotBlueprint
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains a complete specification of a robot. Constructed using the JavaScript GUI. Stored as json strings in database. A vector should be provided to Match.BuildRobots() to create functional Robot objects.
